      "text": "All are connected\nto each other, according to the people\nbuy we will update weight on edge\n\nif anyone come and buy for protend\nwe will see what are the edge\nassociated with protein and higher\nweight, we can recommend that\nin this case we dont need to add manually\nanything system will automatically\nshow the recommendation based on weight",
