      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777295823908,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we willl assign number to each item and then recommend other item which is close to that item\n\napple    1\nbanana   2\nMango    3\nOrange.  4\nGuava.   5\n.\n.\n.\npeach.   100\n\n\nProtein  101\nbcaa     102\nCreatein 103\n.....\n.\n.\nFistOil. 150\n\nBlender   151\nToaster.  152\nCoffee Maker 153",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we willl assign number to each item and then recommend other item which is close to that item\n\napple    1\nbanana   2\nMango    3\nOrange.  4\nGuava.   5\n.\n.\n.\npeach.   100\n\n\nProtein  101\nbcaa     102\nCreatein 103\n.....\n.\n.\nFistOil. 150\n\nBlender   151\nToaster.  152\nCoffee Maker 153",
