      "originalText": "Netflix Movie recommendation system \n\n1 Dhamaal\nrecommend Hera pheri\n\nrecommend Golmal\n\nwe have set of 20 movies, A person love one movie, which movie we will recommend them?\n1 is it comedy movie\n2 is it action movie\n3 is it serious movie according to that we will recommend them",
