      "text": "X-axis action level (-10 for peaceful, +10 for action)\nY-axis comedy level(-10 for serious, +10 for comedy)\n\n\nsuppose for war -> [action, comedy] is [10, -5] this 10, -5 is our vector, these numbers are vectore\nwe have given certain number to a specific thing.\n",
