    {
      "id": "xy0qRqtt3euoB7JTqhZeZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1341.8364635678067,
      "y": 74018.14229379661,
      "width": 1122,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bsy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1443699882,
      "version": 1150,
      "versionNonce": 1866603702,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777372828094,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "the seriious drama(Bottom Left) : Lagaan, Swadesh, Dangal, Tare Zameen par all are clustered togetther\nBut are they really similar?\nLagaan is a historical epic\nSwadesh is a contemporary social drama\nDangal is a biographical sports drama\nTare Zameen Par is an emotional film about childhood\n\nA user who loved Lagaan for its historical scale might be disappointed\ndo yo improve our User experience we will move to more dimentions\n\nUpgrading to 5-Dimentional model\n\nDim1 -> Action level(Same as before)\nDim2 -> Comedu level (same as before)\nDim3 -> emotional drama (-10 for light hearted, +10 for intense)\nDim4 -> Romance level(-10 for no romance, +10 for epic love story)\nDim5 -> Realism (-10 for pure escapism/fantasy, +10 for grounded)\n\nWar -> [10, -5, -4, 2 ,-7]\nthis 5-D can have N dimention, this is vector.  LLamma has upto 4096 dimensions. and this\nvector puts similar things near by. so that it can recommend near by things.\n\n \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "the seriious drama(Bottom Left) : Lagaan, Swadesh, Dangal, Tare Zameen par all are clustered togetther\nBut are they really similar?\nLagaan is a historical epic\nSwadesh is a contemporary social drama\nDangal is a biographical sports drama\nTare Zameen Par is an emotional film about childhood\n\nA user who loved Lagaan for its historical scale might be disappointed\ndo yo improve our User experience we will move to more dimentions\n\nUpgrading to 5-Dimentional model\n\nDim1 -> Action level(Same as before)\nDim2 -> Comedu level (same as before)\nDim3 -> emotional drama (-10 for light hearted, +10 for intense)\nDim4 -> Romance level(-10 for no romance, +10 for epic love story)\nDim5 -> Realism (-10 for pure escapism/fantasy, +10 for grounded)\n\nWar -> [10, -5, -4, 2 ,-7]\nthis 5-D can have N dimention, this is vector.  LLamma has upto 4096 dimensions. and this\nvector puts similar things near by. so that it can recommend near by things.\n\n \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
