      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777692670802,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "I will compare it with everyone(1 billion)\n10 item: distance sabse kam hogi, unko recommed kar dunga\n\n\nThe reason a full scan is slow is because it's perfect. \nIt calculates the distance to every single point and \nguarantees it finds the absolute closest one. \nThis is called Exact Nearest Neighbor (ENN) search.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "I will compare it with everyone(1 billion)\n10 item: distance sabse kam hogi, unko recommed kar dunga\n\n\nThe reason a full scan is slow is because it's perfect. \nIt calculates the distance to every single point and \nguarantees it finds the absolute closest one. \nThis is called Exact Nearest Neighbor (ENN) search.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
